Subject: Unable to login to console in staging environment
Description: Hi, I am Unable to login to console in staging environment. The active directory sync password expired. I need to update that.
What_We_Know__c:
We have reset the user password from the backend to be able to login and make the changes in the System Configuration -> System Settings for the AD Administrators Sync.
The user was able to login after these changes with his AD credentials.
